1) create database 
 use <databasename> 
 ex: use nodedecember21


2) create a collecton in the database you are in(u r now in nodedecember21)
   db.createCollection("products");

3) how to insert a value in a collection. 
db.<collectionname>.insert(<object>)

ex:
db.products.insert({name:"Tshirt",price:2000});

4) how to list values in a collection 

db.<collectionname>.find()

ex: 
db.products.find() 

5) to delete a database run the command
db.dropDatabase()
Note: you should be in the database to run this command and it will delete
the database that you are in .
